(173, 'Silverstone SUGO SG04', '', 'Micro-ATX w/Handle<br />3x3.5" HDD Bays<br />1x5.25" ODD Bays<br />w/430W PSU', 'Sugo represents exquisiteness with its line of beautifully crafted small but powerful TourRig chassis, and SilverStone&#039;s Sugo SG04 is certainly an exquisite chassis.   Adjustable fan positions enable users to devise their own cooling layout as required with the front door helping to reduce noise effectively. Packing with thoughtful features, the SG04 is truly worthy of living up to become another benchmark TourRig enclosure.', 210.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0, '2009-08-26 12:11:34', '', 0.00, '', 0.00, '', 0.00, 0, NULL),
(174, 'Thermaltake LanBox', '', 'Micro-ATX w/Handle<br />3x3.5" HDD Bays<br />2x5.25" ODD Bays<br />w/430W PSU', 'Thermaltake presents a case capable of giving you the power of a desktop with the transportability of a laptop. The handle on this case is not just for show. It will take the weight of your system without worry. The VF1000BWS comes with a 5.25" and a 3.5" external drive bays. To give you plenty of storage, there is also two 3.5" internal drive bays. But what sets it apart is the 7" external drive bay for the express use of an integrated monitor that could be converted to a second 5.25" drive bay if you prefer. \r\n<br /><br />\r\nThe entire case is made of lightweight aluminum to keep carrying the case from becoming a burden. So never worry again about how you&#039;ll get your system to the gig.', 175.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0, '2009-08-26 12:18:38', '', 0.00, '', 0.00, '', 0.00, 1, NULL),
(175, 'NZXT Rogue', '', 'Micro-ATX w/Strap<br />5x3.5" HDD<br />2x5.25" ODD<br />w/430W PSU<br />', 'Introducing the performance gaming SFF chassis from NZXT, the Rogue, built with an 3mm aluminum frame and fitted with the excellent cooling possibilities like three 120mm fans, the Rogue offers the best performance and quality for M-ATX DAW systems. Tailored for computing on the go, the Rogue comes standard with a carrying strap.  All the components inside can are also protected by the sturdy frame and a locking mechanism to insure maximum security. NZXT has designed the Rogue to offer the best cooling, craftsmanship, expandability in this range of chassis.', 120.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0, '2009-08-26 12:19:32', '', 0.00, '', 0.00, '', 0.00, 1, NULL);
