(322, 'Asus 27" LCD Monitor', 'VE278Q ', '<p>1920x1080<br />2ms 300cd/m2<br />ASCR 10,000,000:1</p>', '<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h2>10,000,000:1 ASUS Smart Contrast Ratio</h2>\r\n<p>Dynamically enhances the display&rsquo;s contrast by adjusting the  luminance of the backlight to achieve the darkest black and brightest  white &ndash; delivering lifelike images.<br /><br /></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h2>2ms Response Time</h2>\r\n<p>Quick response time of 2ms (GTG) eliminates ghosting and tracers for  more fluid video playback. <br /><br /></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h2>Full HD with HDMI</h2>\r\n<p>VE278Q leads you to enter a big and spectacular world of colors with  Full HD 1080p (1920x1080) support and HDMI port.<br /><br /></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h2>AI Light for Brightness Optimization</h2>\r\n<p>AI Light function enables the VE278Q automatically adjusting to lower  brightness and make your eyes feel more comfortable in the dim  environment. Furthermore, it helps save more 25% power consumption.<br /><br /></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Rich I/O Ports- Allow Simultaneous Connections to More Video Devices</h2>\r\n<p>Embedded digital HDMI and DisplayPort inputs, VE278Q enables the most  advanced graphic cards/ computers connection. The DisplayPort interface  also offers better support of multiple display streams, longer cable  connection, and interoperability with other inputs, such as VGA, DVI and  HDMI.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Picture in Picture - Display 2 Different Signals Simultaneously</h2>\r\n<p>Need to research on the Internet, but a championship game is about to  start on TV? The VE278Q offers PIP(Picture in Picture) function(via  hotkey) and has the capability to display images of two different  signals at the same time.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<!-- Splendid-->\r\n<h2>Splendid&trade; Video Intelligence Technology</h2>\r\n<p>The exclusive Splendid Video Intelligence Technology optimizes video  performance and image fidelity by enhancing color, brightness, contrast,  and sharpness. 6 preset video modes (Scenery, Theater, Game, Night  View, sRGB and Standard) can be selected via a hotkey.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table width="615px">\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan="2" class="tablehead">Specifications</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>TFT-LCD Panel</td>\r\n<td><strong>Panel Size:</strong> 27" (68.6cm)  Wide  Screen  (16:9) <br /> <strong>True Resolution:</strong> 1920X1080  <br /><strong>Pixel  Pitch:</strong> 0.311mm <br /><strong>Brightness(Max):</strong> 300  cd/&#13217; <br /><strong>Contrast  Ratio (Max.):</strong> 10000000  :1  (ASCR)<br /><strong>Display Color:</strong> 16.7M  <br /><strong>Viewing Angle (CR&#8807;10):</strong> 170&deg;(H)/160&deg;(V) <br /><strong>Response  Time:</strong> 2  ms  (Gray-to-Gray)<br /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Video Features</td>\r\n<td>Trace  Free Technology<br />SPLENDID Video Intelligence Technology<br />SPLENDID  Video Preset Modes (6 modes)<br />Skin-Tone Selection (3 mode)<br />Picture-in-Picture<br />Color  Temperature Selection(4 modes)<br /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Audio Features</td>\r\n<td>Stereo  Speakers 3Wx2 stereo RMS <br /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Convenient Hotkey</td>\r\n<td>SPLENDID  Video Preset Mode Selection<br />Auto. Adjustment<br />Brightness  Adjustment<br />Volume Adjustment<br />Picture-in-Picture<br />Input Selection<br /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Input / Output</td>\r\n<td><strong>PC Input:</strong> DisplayPort/DVI-D/D-Sub<br /><strong>PC Audio Input:</strong> 3.5mm Mini-jack <br /><strong>Video  Input:</strong> HDMI<br /><strong>AV Audio Input:</strong> HDMI <br /><strong>Earphone jack:</strong> 3.5mm Mini-jack <br /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Signal Frequency</td>\r\n<td><strong>Analog  Signal Frequency:</strong> 24~92kHz (H)/ 50~85 Hz (V)  <br /><strong>Digital Signal  Frequency:</strong> 24~92kHz (H)/ 50~85 Hz (V)  <br /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Power  Consumption</td>\r\n<td>Power Consumption &lt;  45  W <br />Power Saving Mode  &lt;  2  W</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Mechanical Design</td>\r\n<td><strong>Chassis  Colors:</strong> Black<br /><strong>Tilt:</strong> +20&deg;~ -5&deg; <br /><strong>VESA Wall Mounting:</strong> 100x100mm <br /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Security</td>\r\n<td>Kensington lock<br /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Dimension  (WxHxD mm)</td>\r\n<td>Phys.Dimension(WxHxD):  643x445.6x220mm<br />Box  Dimension(WxHxD):  732x560x176mm<br /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Weight</td>\r\n<td>Net  Weight (Esti.):  6.5  kg <br />Gross Weight (Esti.):  9.8  kg</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Accessory</td>\r\n<td>DVI  cable<br />VGA cable<br />Audio cable<br />Power cord<br />Quick start guide<br />warranty  card<br /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Regulation Approval</td>\r\n<td>Energy Star&reg;,  UL/cUL, CB, CE, EuP, FCC, CCC, BSMI, Gost-R, C-Tick, VCCI, PSB, EK,  J-MOSS, Taiwan Green Mark, RoHS, WEEE,  Windows 7 &amp; Vista WHQL</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</table>', 370.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.25, 0, '2010-10-27 06:35:25', '', 0.00, '', 0.00, '', 0.00, 1, NULL),
(323, 'Smart Drive NEO', '', '<p>Silent HDD Enclosure<br />5.25" to 3.5" Adapter</p>', '<p>The SMART DRIVE NEO is the most feature-rich and sophisticated 5.25" hard disk silencer case/enclosure - it is a premium quality product for customers who demand the best.&nbsp;&nbsp;The Smart Drive NEO is a new generation of HDD silencer, which will reduce hard disk noise, vibration and operating temperatures, aiding computer longevity, and supporting optimal HDD performance.</p>\r\n<h3>Smart Drive Neo - Hard Disk Drive (HDD) Enclosure Features:</h3>\r\n<li>Insulated vibration framework</li>\r\n<li>Constructed from sound absorbing material</li>\r\n<li>Active vibration suppression</li>\r\n<li>Thick steel top cover to reduce vibration (1.6mm steel - NEO Model)</li>\r\n<li>Dust free and waterproof</li>', 80.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.05, 0, '2010-12-11 21:08:57', '2x ', 160.00, '3x ', 240.00, '4x', 320.00, 1, NULL),
(324, 'HDD Noise Reduction System', '', '<p>Rubber HDD Mounts<br />5.25" to 3.5" Adapter</p>', '<p>This item is made up of two large silicon rubber blocks with embedded steel plates. One is installed on each side of the hard drive and then the unit is installed in a 5.25" drive bay. The rubber blocks will then help inhibit vibrations from the hard drive reaching the case. A must buy for anyone looking to make their case quieter!&nbsp;</p>', 20.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0, '2010-12-11 21:38:17', '2x ', 40.00, '3x', 60.00, '4x', 80.00, 1, NULL),
(325, 'Trayless Mobile Rack', '', '<p>Screwless for fast mounting<br /> Anti-Shock Absorber System</p>', '<p>The trayless mobile rack is for use with 3.5" SATA I/II hard drive. The storage capacity of the hard drive is unlimited. With its tray-less and screwless design it provides fast and easy installation. The anti-vibration air cushion design gives hard drive an extra protection from damage and reduces noise. The trayless mobile rack comes with a Security key-lock prevents intrusion and theft to the most important data.</p>', 30.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0, '2010-12-12 00:40:04', '2x', 60.00, '3x', 90.00, '', 0.00, 1, NULL),
