lity</h2>\r\n<p><strong>Interface</strong>: Works with ASIO, Core Audio, WDM, MME, and multi-client drivers.</p>\r\n<h2>What&rsquo;s Included</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Mbox Pro interface</li>\r\n<li>Drivers installation disc</li>\r\n<li>FireWire cable</li>\r\n<li>Mbox quick setup guide</li>\r\n<li>Registration card</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 719.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 6, '2011-11-17 16:59:59', '', 0.00, '', 0.00, '', 0.00, 1, 'Brand::Avid,,Form Factor::Portable,,Format::Firewire,,Total Inputs::8,,Total Outputs::8,,Analog Inputs::6,,Analog Outputs::6,,Digital I/O::2/2,,MIDI I/O::1/1,,Microphone Preamps::4,,Sample Rate::192kHz,,Headphone outs::2,,Included Software::');
