(384, 'M-Audio Fast Track', '', '<p>24Bit/48kHz<br />2x2 Channels<br />USB 2.0 Portable<br /><br /></p>', '<ul class="tabnav">\r\n<li><a href="#overview">Overview</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="#features">Features</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="#specifications">Specifications</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div class="tabcontent">\r\n<div class="overview">\r\n<p>Turn your computer into a powerful music production studio with the M-Audio&reg; Fast Track&reg;&mdash;the best-selling recording interface in its category. Featuring a simple "plug-and-play" USB connection, Fast Track is the easiest way to record guitar, vocals and more with your PC or Mac. Simply plug in your instruments and you&rsquo;re ready to rock. Fast Track even offers phantom power so you can use professional-quality studio condenser microphones like the M-Audio Nova&reg;.</p>\r\n<p>Fast Track is compatible with most popular music recording applications from GarageBand to studio-standard Pro Tools, and includes easy-to-use Pro Tools SE recording and effects software so you can start making music immediately.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="features">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>2-input, 2-output audio interface</li>\r\n<li>compatible with most popular recording software including Pro Tools*</li>\r\n<li>24-bit/48kHz professional sound quality</li>\r\n<li>plug-and-play USB connection (USB 2.0 compatible)</li>\r\n<li>XLR microphone input with gain control and 48V phantom power</li>\r\n<li>1/4" instrument input with gain control</li>\r\n<li>1/4" stereo headphone output</li>\r\n<li>RCA stereo speaker outputs</li>\r\n<li>output level knob for adjusting volume of headphones and speaker outputs</li>\r\n<li>direct monitoring button</li>\r\n<li>powered by USB&mdash;no power adapter required</li>\r\n<li>includes easy-to-use Pro Tools SE software\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>studio-standard recording, editing and mixing features</li>\r\n<li>features powerful effects like reverb, delay and more to polish your mixes</li>\r\n<li>includes Structure&reg; Essential virtual instrument</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>comprehensive loop library&mdash;perfect for quickly constructing song ideas</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="specifications">\r\n<h2>Compatibility</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>ASIO 2</li>\r\n<li>WDM</li>\r\n<li>Mac OS X Core Audio</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Minimum System Requirements (PC)</h2>\r\n<p><strong>Fast Track (hardware only)</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Windows XP (SP3)* / Windows Vista (32Bit , 64 Bit) / Win7 (32Bit , 64 Bit)</li>\r\n<li>Pentium 4 2.0GHz</li>\r\n<li>1GB RAM</li>\r\n<li>one native USB port</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>*Home and Professional Edition only. Windows Media Center Edition is not supported.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Pro Tools SE software</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>1.8 GHz multi-core processor (Intel or AMD)</li>\r\n<li>5400 RPM drive</li>\r\n<li>Windows XP Home (SP3 or greater), Windows XP Pro (SP3 or greater), Windows 7 Home Premium, Windows 7 Professional, or Windows 7 Ultimate</li>\r\n<li>2 GB RAM for Windows 7 64-bit; 1 GB RAM for XP or Windows 7 32-bit</li>\r\n<li>Adobe Flash Player 10</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><i>Note: Other supported audio applications may have higher minimum system requirements.</i></p>\r\n<h2>Minimum System Requirements (Mac)</h2>\r\n<p><strong>Fast Track (hardware only)</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>OS X 10.4.11</li>\r\n<li>G4 processor**</li>\r\n<li>1GB RAM</li>\r\n<li>one native USB port</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>** G4 accelerator cards not supported.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Pro Tools SE software</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>1.8 GHz multi-core processor (Intel)</li>\r\n<li>5400 RPM drive</li>\r\n<li>1 GB RAM</li>\r\n<li>Mac OS X 10.5.8 or greater, or 10.6.1 or greater</li>\r\n<li>Adobe Flash Player 10</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><i>Note: Other supported audio applications may have higher minimum system requirements.</i></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 119.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0, '2011-11-17 18:33:46', '', 0.00, '', 0.00, '', 0.00, 1, 'Brand::M-Audio,,Form Factor::Portable,,Format::USB 2.0,,Total Inputs::2,,Total 